Schmallenberg virus also prevalent in Slovenia
----------------------------------------------
The presence of Schmallenberg virus in sheep in Slovenia has been confirmed. This has been reported by the Veterinary Chamber. Schmallenberg Virus was 1st discovered in 2011 in Germany and since then the disease has spread rapidly in northern and western Europe.

